1246
01:23:13,421 --> 01:23:14,581
M. Waldo.

1247
01:23:14,741 --> 01:23:15,982
M. Sikorsky.

1248
01:23:16,141 --> 01:23:18,661
Navré de vous interrompre mais j'ai du nouveau.

1249
01:23:18,821 --> 01:23:21,101
